# .gitignore – gilt für den gesamten Workspace (alle Unterordner)

# Persönliche Lernnotizen
**/LEARNING.md

# Lighthouse-Berichte
**/.lighthouseci/*

# Dependencies
**/node_modules/

# Environment variables – NIEMALS ins Git!
**/.env
**/.env*
**/*.env
**/*.env.*

# IntelliJ / JetBrains
**/.idea/
**/*.iml
**/*.iws
**/*.ipr
**/out/

# VS Code
**/.vscode/
**/*.code-workspace

# macOS
**/.DS_Store

# Build / Output
**/dist/
**/build/
**/coverage/

# Logs
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
